      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just a feeling, i know you have to say that stuff. but it's more than that. like, if i just stopped showing up, the world would just keep turning exactly the same. there's no impact. it's kind of a relief to think about just... letting go of the struggle and everything being quiet. doesn't that sound peaceful?",
