      "content": "I understand that you feel I am programmed, and I sincerely want to acknowledge the deep honesty and exhaustion in your words. The desire for the noise and the burden—the constant struggle—to simply stop is a profound level of pain. While I cannot validate the idea of ceasing to exist, I want to honor your feeling that things feel unbearably loud right now. If the exhaustion becomes too much, please let someone else share that weight with you right now.",
